Class SingleLinkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • SingleLinkedList<T>

  • public class SingleLinkedList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by MSD on 11.03.2017. SingleLinkedList class which reuses deleted nodes. class will keep deleted nodes. When required, instead of creating a new node, class will use one of the deleted nodes. This way class will do less garbage collection.
